7. Speller infrastructure

aSpell

Write documentation here as well.

Munch-list is working, see above. Needs more affixes before it is useful, cf the size discussion. See previous meeting memo.

MS Office spellers

Nothing new, see previous meeting memo.

OpenOffice.org

Requires MySpell (probably hunspell and even Aspell in the future), we want to maintain only one main source file for all spellers. Others are doing it, the question is only how. This is the goal to be investigated by Børre and Tomi.

For pointers, see the previous meeting memo.
